Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about training an Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR) system using noisy transcriptions. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses a deep neural network for sequence-to-sequence modeling. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with improving the accuracy of an ASR system using a new loss function. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with improving the performance of a speech recognition system.
